<headline>Special Weather Statement issued November 27 at 4:38PM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...A band of heavy snow will move southeastward across
northwestern Beaverhead County...
A band of heavy snow will pass southeastward over the next hour or
two. Sudden reduction of visibility to a quarter mile or less will
be possible. Expect variable driving conditions, especially near
the band of snow. Overall, snow should last for an hour or so
before dissipating.</description>
